textAnnotations.description:
-2OLNCJR A DEEP
Integraph, a Mechanicai Integrator.
Coradi Werke, Zürich Switzerlaand 1916.
Inventor Br. Abdank-Abakanowicz
This device provides the circumference, area, and
other values over a complex drafted figure.
More detailed explanations are being developed
jointly with emeriti faculty at the ETH Züriet
